description: ByteScout PDF To HTML SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX
releaseNotes:
ByteScout PDF To HTML SDK converts PDF to HTML without any additional software required.
        
ByteScout, Inc. (c) 2008-2019.

Compatibility: .NET Framework 2.0 or later; .NET Core 2.0 or later.
Works with: .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX, Visual Basic 6, Classic ASP, Delphi and others.

Benefits:

- Converts PDF to HTML with layout preserved;
- Text styles are preserved;
- Vector graphics is preserved (as background image);
- Precise positioning of text and images is supported to reproduce the original PDF document design;
- Doesn't require Adobe Reader or any other 3rd-party software to be installed;
- Works with .NET Framework 2.0 and later;
- Provides ActiveX interface to use from traditional programming languages (VC++, VB6, Delphi) and scripting (VBscript, JScript and others).
